---
const {
  title = "AKOMARO 歐洲品牌雜誌",
  description = "精選歐洲品牌、生活風格、故事與選品內容。",
  image = "/images/og-default.svg",
  canonical = "https://magazine.akomar.com/"
} = Astro.props;
---
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description} />
  <link rel="canonical" href={canonical} />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
  <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
  <meta property="og:url" content={canonical} />
  <meta property="og:image" content={image.startsWith("http") ? image : `https://magazine.akomar.com${image}`} />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/global.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="top-utility">
    <div class="container top-utility-inner">
      <div class="utility-nav">
        <a href="#">登入 / 訂閱</a>
        <a href="/brands">品牌</a>
        <a href="/about">關於</a>
        <a href="/enquiry">聯絡</a>
      </div>
      <div class="utility-social">
        <a href="#">Facebook</a>
        <a href="#">Instagram</a>
        <a href="#">Threads</a>
        <a href="#">YouTube</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <header class="brand-header">
    <div class="container brand-header-inner">
      <div class="brand-block">
        <div class="brand-title">AKOMARO</div>
        <div class="brand-subtitle">EUROPEAN BRANDS</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="main-nav-wrap">
    <div class="container main-nav-inner">
      <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="/" class="active">首頁</a>
        <a href="/category/beauty">美妝保養</a>
        <a href="/category/fashion">服裝配飾</a>
        <a href="/category/wellness">健康保健</a>
        <a href="/category/home">居家生活</a>
        <a href="/category/food">食品飲品</a>
        <a href="/brands">更多</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="main-nav-right">⌕</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main>
    <slot />
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container site-footer-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="footer-brand">AKOMARO</div>
        <div class="footer-brand-sub">EUROPEAN BRANDS</div>
        <p class="footer-text">
          AKOMARO 以雜誌式方式介紹歐洲品牌、生活風格、產品系列與品牌故事，
          並承接訂閱、查詢及訂單需求。
        </p>
        <p class="footer-text">聯絡我們：contact@akomar.com</p>
        <div class="footer-social">
          <a href="#">f</a>
          <a href="#">ig</a>
          <a href="#">th</a>
          <a href="#">yt</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="footer-heading">更多內容</h3>
        <div class="footer-mini-list">
          <div class="footer-mini-item">
            <img src="/images/cover-asia.svg" alt="thumb" />
            <div>最新歐洲品牌故事與系列介紹</div>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-mini-item">
            <img src="/images/cover-signals.svg" alt="thumb" />
            <div>適合亞洲市場的生活風格選品</div>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-mini-item">
            <img src="/images/cover-insights.svg" alt="thumb" />
            <div>品牌內容、訂閱與分發整合</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="footer-heading">熱門分類</h3>
        <div class="footer-text">美妝保養</div>
        <div class="footer-text">服裝配飾</div>
        <div class="footer-text">健康保健</div>
        <div class="footer-text">母嬰親子</div>
        <div class="footer-text">寵物生活</div>
        <div class="footer-text">食品飲品</div>
        <div class="footer-text">居家生活</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <div class="container footer-bottom-inner">
        <div>© AKOMARO</div>
        <div class="footer-nav">
          <a href="/brands">品牌</a>
          <a href="/about">關於</a>
          <a href="/enquiry">聯絡</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
